summary: It's time to celebrate 🍾 I can't believe I have 2.2k followers, y'all! Thank you SO MUCH for following this silly disaster of a...
body:
It’s time to celebrate 🍾 I can’t believe I have 2.2k followers, y'all! Thank you SO MUCH for following this silly disaster of a blog!

-

I’ve put some thought into how I want to do this and I’m hoping y'all will enjoy this plan! You do not have to be following me to participate, though feel free 🍭

-

Part 1: Gif/Picture drabbles

I will take TEN NINE EIGHT SEVEN SIX FIVE FOUR THREE picture/gif submissions and write a drabble about each. If the gif/picture isn’t clear on who it is (for example, a gif of two people kissing that is not one of the characters) please let me know who you want me to write about.

  • I will take submissions for:
  1. Steve Rogers (x reader)
  2. Chris Evans (x reader)
  3. Evanstan
  4. Sebastian Stan (x reader)
  5. Bucky Barnes (x reader)
  6. Stucky
  7. Steggy
  8. Buckynat

I will take submissions for one week. After next Sunday, if I’ve received 10, I will close submissions. Reader can be male, female, gender neutral. I’m open to all! They can be angst, fluff, smut, anything! You could also send me something random ( a cup of coffee) and a pairing and I can work off that!

Part 2: Prompts

For those of you who would like to write for this, you’ll find ten prompts below. They’re random, which is all the more fun sometimes. Please send me an ask with your prompt and your pairing. It can be any of the above listed under pic/gif submissions. Minimum word count: 200. No due date, write at your own leisure. Please tag me when you upload it and use the tag #CRB2200. I can’t wait to read them! 🥂

UPDATE: so I didn’t realize so many people would wanna write for the prompts so I’m saying it’s okay for more than one person to claim one of these prompts. If you don’t like that let me know but I think it’ll be fun to read everyone’s take on these prompts! 😃

  1. Moonlight @musette22 @twittytelly
  2. Life after divorce @what-would-carol-danvers-do (Stucky)
  3. Man bun @wintersoldier1989
  4. Chocolate muffin @ginabaker1666 (Steve x reader)
  5. “Nailed it!” @stanclub (Chris x reader)
  6. Cabin @mom—nicole (Stucky)
  7. Wrong number @stuck-y-together (Stucky)
  8. “Don’t say a word.” @captainmarvelsbitch @thebestpersonherelovesbucky
  9. Pastry chef @robotskilledmygrandma
  10. “Have we met before?” @supersoldiersruined-me (Chris x reader) & @cevansgirl (Chris x reader)

Part 3: Chris Evans oneshot

So poll results are in!

A: 29 (first time anal CE x Reader)

B: 29 (lack of pullout CE x Reader)

C: 18 (Meet cute at Dog Park CE x Reader)

I’ve gotta be honest, I’m currently feeling B more than A but we’ll see 👀🤔 This will be posted by March 31st!

–

Again, thank you all so much for following, reading, sending asks and interacting! 💜 A signal boost would be appreciated 💜 Tagging some mutuals who might be interested:

@what-would-carol-danvers-do @stanclub @buckysbrat @supersmuttyqueernerd @tillsunbeamsfindyou @freshwoods @onehotgreasymechanic @buckmesideways22 @twittytelly @ginabaker1666 @thebestpersonherelovesbucky @wintersoldier1989 @mom—nicole @kawairinrin @anyoneforteaus @ravensonata @captainmarvelsbitch

[Natasha turns the tablet screen around to show him Wakanda's...
body:
Tony: Hey, Nat. Can you give me a gander of the environs?

[Natasha turns the tablet screen around to show him Wakanda’s view]

Tony: Wow! This place looks beautif…

[They all hear him pause]

Bucky: Wait for it.

[Natasha touches the non-StarkPad screen]

Natasha: He’s frozen.

Steve: [groans] Same thing happened last night at the worst possible time. I had just gotten on all fours and taken off my panti…

[Steve freezes]

Clint: Now Cap’s frozen.
